## Conclusion

**ScheduleSync aims to fundamentally improve the way university students coordinate group activities by making it simple, fast, and visual to find mutual free time and plan events. Unlike existing tools, it centers the social experience within the calendar, providing a solution for real-life student pain points with a modern, privacy-aware, and real-time web application.**

